    <summary>Let your visitors do your marketing while you sleep! &#xD;
Adds product-specific share buttons for several social networks to your product display pages. Works great with the analytics provided by Pinterest etc. to analyse return traffic.</summary>
    <description>Always looks beautiful at any screen size and resolution, by using Font-Awesome (aka Twitter Bootstrap) font-icons.&#xD;
Very lean footprint with no additional javascript loaded. &#xD;
Choose any subset of Facebook, Google+, LinkedIn, Pinterest, Twitter (both share and follow).&#xD;
Choice of 2 shapes for each button. All stylable, change colour, position, size, spacing ...&#xD;
Pinterest button &#x201C;pins&#x201D; the image belonging to the product viewed.</description>
    <notes>For facebook, Pinterest, Google+, Twitter and LinkedIn.</notes>
